### Turn ON Meeting Room Light (SwitchBot - Cloud API)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/devices/command
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deviceID": "light_meeting01",
  "command": "turnOn"
}

### Turn OFF Meeting Room Light
POST http://localhost:3000/api/devices/command
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deviceID": "light_meeting01",
  "command": "turnOff"
}

### Set Showroom AC (Nature Remo - Local API)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/devices/command
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deviceID": "ac_showroom01",
  "command": "setTemp24"
}

### Start Roomba Cleaning (MQTT)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/devices/command
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deviceID": "roomba01",
  "command": "start"
}

### Test invalid device (should return 400 error)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/devices/command
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deviceID": "nonexistent_device",
  "command": "turnOn"
}